## Selectors Reference

| Element | Selector | Notes |
|---------|----------|-------|
| Title | `textarea[placeholder="Title"]` | `.value` + input/change events |
| Subtitle | `textarea[placeholder*="subtitle"]` | `.value` + input/change events |
| Body editor | `div[contenteditable="true"]` (first one) | Paste approach, clear first |
| Save status | button text "Saved" | Auto-saves after edits |
| Continue | button text "Continue" | Opens publish settings panel |
| Audience radio | `input[type="radio"][value="everyone"]` (first) | First radio group |
| Comments radio | `input[type="radio"][value="everyone"]` (second) | Second radio group - MUST be Everyone |
| Tag input | `input[placeholder="Select or create tags"]` | Type tag name, click "Create" option |
| Publish | button text "Send to everyone now" or "Publish now" | Free pubs show "Publish now" |
| Subscribe dialog | button text "Publish without buttons" | May appear after Publish click |
| Email dialog | button text "Also send via email" | May appear after subscribe dialog |
| Dashboard | `{{handle}}.substack.com/publish/home` | Lists posts, drafts |
| Create post | button text "Create post" (on dashboard) | Opens new editor |
| New post nav | button text "New post" | Opens Notes composer, NOT article editor |
